snippet: Elena Delle Donne of the Chicago Sky became the first rookie to lead the W.N.B.A. All-Star voting when the starters were announced Thursday.
abstract: Elena Delle Donne of Chicago Sky becomes first rookie to lead WNBA All-Star voting; other basketball news noted.
